com.fluidops.ajax.FEventListener
public class FComboboxInput
extends FSubjectPredicateBasedInput

Dropdown-based input field for fixed subject and predicate. Supports both literals and URIs as input, where the choice can be configured via query or input string.

Description copied from class: FStatementInput
Clones the current object, while possibly copying the init subject, predicate, and object according to the configuration. The current values are not considered, i.e. will be blank for the cloned object.
